{"tid":511992,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟人要有幾戇鳩先會信風水依樣嘢","createTime":"2017-12-28T04:44:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T04:31:31.000Z","uid":34223,"like":25,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"510636300549ad0c57fea830678d8f105a42bbc4","tid":511992,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:44:13.000Z","msg":"是咁的 我腦細今日叫咗個戇鳩風水佬上嚟公司睇風水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又話乜撚嘢要擺陣呀又話要擺乜嘢金杯呀咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好撚心你啦 21世紀都仲信風水依家嘢 戇鳩鳩生勾勾咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n晒時間睇風水都唔撚諗下點解間公司越做越頹 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就睇下公司幾時收皮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc7954b042b5a14a4997ee2ff3dad51afb209883","tid":511992,"uid":34223,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:45:05.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"fe30874c418a2a7083a7f655940fa849bbaece37","tid":511992,"uid":150611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:45:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c5cbe4087af3d81ec6504d91fef8491effdf27cf","tid":511992,"uid":48796,"like":6,"dislike":3,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:45:51.000Z","msg":"你覺得澳門賭場有冇風水陣"},{"pid":"3fd5254f17ab7234511fb47be9ed803701a574a1","tid":511992,"uid":85819,"like":5,"dislike":9,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T04:49:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e1657b644f7b0bbdadc41f05d4dd40bfa70ad01c","tid":511992,"uid":41355,"like":0,"dislike":