oji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0b959cf3ce1d906da02df1395d1c02071fbc85","tid":511992,"uid":161230,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T06:48:52.000Z","msg":"我覺得風水唔多唔少有影響<br />\n風水=統計學+環境學+心理學。其實可以更多<br />\n你放盆花/水 其實會令空氣更好。空氣好人都健康啲<br />\n<br />\n放銅錢會影響磁場。磁場又係會影響人體<br />\n<br />\n心理=有時你用左風水會令你自我感覺良好"},{"pid":"9011096e1d768d256611b1d3e04abda169b3f97e","tid":511992,"uid":123308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T07:05:16.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"6230c9a052d192313cf8759caea5e0c035adf8ec","tid":511992,"uid":34286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T07:09:04.000Z","msg":"禁on9都做到你老細，你要俾佢點"},{"pid":"c76d0178e615f4acc15edad3e6fbdb009d8211b9","tid":511992,"uid":65686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T07:14:11.000Z","msg":"認真回答：<br />\n<br />\n風水如果用作改運/擋煞等用途，我認為係有 認知偏差  嘅（參見<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%AA%8D%E7%9F%A5%E5%81%8F%E8%AA%A4%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8）。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%259F%25A5%25E5%2581%258F%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%25A1%25A8%EF%BC%89%E3%80%82&d=3Q0axaAZ8itZuAOIHRvp%2Fdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=86d78aaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E8%AA%8D%E7%9F%A5%E5%81%8F%E8%AA%A4%E5%88%97%E8%A1%A8）。</a><br />\n<br />\n如果風水係用作建築格局佈置，咁我認為風水都只不過係建築學嘅簡單知識普及，即係話好多風水學裡頭嘅 不宜/宜 都係建築學裡頭揾得到理論支撐，唔需要太過將風水神化。<br />\n<br />\n我認為 風水 傳承落來係唔完整嘅，同埋呢一行良莠不齊，所以我唔盡信，亦都因為我又證明唔到佢唔啱，證明唔到佢冇效。"},{"pid":"1fec17ff040fc645ab1a1f61ed94e65ab185f54d","tid":511992,"uid":138420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a0b959cf3ce1d906da02df1395d1c02071fbc85","tid":511992,"uid":161230,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T06:48:52.000Z","msg":"我覺得風水唔多唔少有影響<br />\n風水=統計學+環境學+心理學。其實可以更多<br />\n你放盆花/水 其實會令空氣更好。空氣好人都健康啲<br />\n<br />\n放銅錢會影響磁場。磁場又係會影響人體<br />\n<br />\n心理=有時你用左風水會令你自我感覺良好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-28T13:28:33.000Z","msg":"你知唔知咩係磁場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n心理咪姐係自我欺騙 我洗鬼俾錢咩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e40310f8cdf2d978ff67ef20b6f5560c3c383c97","tid":511992,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T01:41:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}